        "collapsible_row-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What's your return policy?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>In case you receive a product that has been damaged during shipment we will automatically ship out new product for you or issue a full refund. Refer to refund policy on footer of page. If you cancel a non subscription before the order is confirmed to ship you will be issued a full refund. Subscription items can be referred to in subscription policy in footer.</p>",
